# Welcome to TAB

TAB just finished setting up this clone. Kick-off is done; you're ready.

## What you're reading

This is an inbox entry. The inbox (`_inbox/`) is where TAB drops work
items and notifications for you. When you finish one, move it to
`_inbox/done/`. You can also ask TAB to "process the inbox" and it will
walk you through any open entries.

## Two things to know

- `.claude/session-transcript.md` is where TAB's reasoning is logged in
  real time. Keep it open in your editor. That's how you see what TAB
  is thinking.
- Close a session by telling TAB "let's wrap up" or running `/dsm-wrap-up`.

You can talk to TAB the way you'd talk to a collaborator. The slash
commands are shortcuts, not requirements.

